When you open the add-card dialog, it copies deck and card of the currently reviewed card (if any)

To report bug, and for more informations, please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-copy-currentcard-in-add-card

<strong>SUPPORT THIS ADD-ON</strong>

Think about giving a <a href="https://ankiweb.net/shared/review/676957592" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://milchior.fr/rate.svg"> thumbs up</a> and about sharing it.